Contract templates


These are defined contract templates, that can be used for easier 
contract signing 

place:

Administration / Contract Templates

template
   - name
   - contract lenght(months)
   - service/s -  selecting one(or more) services with their promotions
     - serivices/coupon suggest - helps choosing a service/service with coupon
     - reqired devices for the service
     - optional devices
     - optional models of the devices
   - adddtional charges - value added services 

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
example:

   name: Internet 30Mbps & Basic TV - 6 x 12.00, 6 x 24.00
   service: Internet 30Mbps & Basic TV
   coupon: Internet 30Mbps & Basic TV 6 monhts 50% (code 2494334)
    required device:
              PON / model: Huawei HG8245T / sell price 24,00
              STB / no model defined
              STB / no model defined
   additional charges : Installation Fee 24.00


